tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE neural_network_changes (
   change_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
   network_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
   architecture TEXT,
   hyperparameters JSON,
   change_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE neural_network_architectures (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    architecture_name VARCHAR(100),
    architecture_details TEXT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE hyperparameters (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    parameter_name VARCHAR(100),
    parameter_value VARCHAR(100),
    architecture_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (architecture_id) REFERENCES neural_network_architectures(id)
)

CREATE TABLE changes_tracking (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    change_description TEXT,
    changed_at TIMESTAMP,
    architecture_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (architecture_id) REFERENCES neural_network_architectures(id)
)

CREATE TABLE version_control (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    version_number VARCHAR(20),
    commit_message TEXT,
    commit_hash VARCHAR(40),
    committed_at TIMESTAMP,
    architecture_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (architecture_id) REFERENCES neural_network_architectures(id)
)
